      "body" : "To be clear, this isn't a failure to build Bitcoin with system dependencies, it's a failure to build Boost. My own need was for working on the depends build itself (namely bumping Qt) without going through the whole gitian setup. I didn't see this as the common case which is why I didn't base against 0.11. The gitian environment will be affected too if it's ever updated. Feel free to close if bumping Boost is the preferred way to go; I just wanted to make the problem and one solution known.",
